NodeWhitelist

NodeWhitelist is a permissions node based whitelist to allow for more flexibility, and the ability for none whitelisted players to go on your server and have a look around.

Contributing

I am happy to accept contributions. To do so, just make a fork on GitHub of NodeWhitelist, make your changes, and submit a pull request. I'll be happy to look it over, and merge it with NodeWhitelist if it all checks out ok. 

By submitting your code to NodeWhitelist, you agree to license your submitted code under the GNU General Public License V3.